# SuisenSha — Recommend + LLM + RAG Pipeline

A production-style recommendation prototype combining **embedding similarity**, **transformer sequential recommendation (SASRec)**, and **RAG-augmented LLM generation** — all evaluated on the MovieLens-100K dataset.

## Architecture

```
                     ┌───────────────────────┐
                     │  Phase 1: Data & EDA  │
                     │  MovieLens-100K       │
                     └──────────┬────────────┘
                                │
            ┌───────────────────┼───────────────────┐
            ▼                   ▼                   ▼
   ┌────────────────┐  ┌────────────────┐  ┌────────────────┐
   │ Phase 2:       │  │ Phase 3:       │  │ Phase 4:       │
   │ Embedding      │  │ SASRec         │  │ RAG + LLM      │
   │ + FAISS        │  │ Transformer    │  │ Generation     │
   └───────┬────────┘  └───────┬────────┘  └───────┬────────┘
           └───────────────────┼───────────────────┘
                               ▼
                    ┌──────────────────────┐
                    │ Phase 5: Evaluation  │
                    │ & Comparison         │
                    └──────────────────────┘
```

## Project Structure

```
SuisenSha/
├── src/
│   └── pipeline/
│       ├── __init__.py
│       ├── __main__.py          # python -m pipeline
│       ├── cli.py               # CLI entry point
│       ├── config.py            # Frozen dataclass configs
│       ├── data/
│       │   └── loader.py        # Phase 1 — download, EDA, sequences
│       ├── models/
│       │   ├── embedding.py     # Phase 2 — Sentence-Transformer + FAISS
│       │   ├── sequential.py    # Phase 3 — SASRec (PyTorch)
│       │   └── rag.py           # Phase 4 — Retrieval + DistilGPT-2
│       └── evaluation/
│           └── metrics.py       # Phase 5 — HR, NDCG, comparison chart
├── tests/
│   ├── test_metrics.py
│   └── test_data_loader.py
├── data/                        # Downloaded dataset (gitignored)
├── artifacts/                   # Model checkpoints, FAISS index
├── outputs/                     # EDA plots, comparison chart
├── pyproject.toml               # PEP 621 packaging + tool config
├── Makefile                     # Dev shortcuts
├── .gitignore
└── README.md
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Install (editable, with dev tools)
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# 2. Run the full pipeline
python -m pipeline.cli

# 3. Run a specific phase
python -m pipeline.cli --phase 1   # Data Loading & EDA
python -m pipeline.cli --phase 2   # Embedding Recommender
python -m pipeline.cli --phase 3   # SASRec Transformer
python -m pipeline.cli --phase 4   # RAG + LLM
python -m pipeline.cli --phase 5   # Evaluation & Comparison

# 4. Run tests
pytest
```

## Pipelines

| Phase | Module | Description |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| 1 | `data.loader` | Downloads MovieLens-100K, runs EDA, builds user sequences |
| 2 | `models.embedding` | Sentence-Transformer embeddings + FAISS similarity search |
| 3 | `models.sequential` | SASRec — causal self-attention for next-item prediction |
| 4 | `models.rag` | FAISS retrieval + DistilGPT-2 for explained recommendations |
| 5 | `evaluation.metrics` | HitRate@k, NDCG@k — comparison across all pipelines |

## Dev Tools

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `make install` | Install production deps |
| `make dev` | Install with dev deps (pytest, ruff, mypy) |
| `make lint` | Run ruff linter |
| `make test` | Run pytest suite |
| `make type-check` | Run mypy |
| `make clean` | Remove caches and data |

## Outputs

- `outputs/eda_distributions.png` — rating, user, and item distribution histograms
- `outputs/comparison.png` — metric comparison bar chart across pipelines
- `artifacts/` — FAISS index, item embeddings, SASRec checkpoint
